rups do not abound plentifully in this game.  And lastly, do not be afraid to pick up new weapons.  Even if you have your favorite ultimate badass gun, it will do you no good if you don't have any ammo for it.  When deciding between which weapon to carry with you, think about how much ammo it carries, and effective damage.  I've dropped a mercury bowgun which kills with one shot usually in order to take a plasma rifle on many occasions simply because the bowgun only gets two shots per clip compared to the rifles 10 shots, and the rate of fire on the bowgun is horribly slow.  Like one shot every 5 seconds or so.  <br>
<br>
Digital Infusion - I feel like I just wrote a review for the damn game.  It is terribly fun though. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/udmario.showPublicProfile?language=EN>dmario</A></span><br> <b>Member</b><br> <font color=#336699>(2/13/01 8:41:51 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/blackanimenet/pk/icon.jpg width=95 height=95></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_smile.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Oni</span><hr size=1> I played it at EB, and I was amazed, the only thing I could gripe about was those strange controls... <p><a href="http://www.geocities.com/blackanimenet"><img src="http://www.geocities.com/blackanimenet/splashimages/button03.gif" border="0"> | Join the Black Anime Network</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/ushousetsu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shousetsu</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.geocities.com/shousetsu_1999/animation.gif width=15 height=15 BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <b>PhotoshopMod</b><br> <font color=#336699>(2/13/01 11:57:06 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/shousetsu_1999/room.jpg width=120 height=78></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_smile.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Oni</span><hr size=1> I think its only playable on PC, you NEED a mouse for controls like that. Its one of the main reasons Rainbow 6 blew on the Playstation, those kinds of games are only playable with a mouse.<br>
